User Stories

1. As a user, I want to improve my memory so I can reduce my risk for dementia.
2. As a user, I want an alternative to television so I can improve the quality of my leisure time.
3. As a user, I want an affordable game so I can spend money on other things.
4. As a user, I want a portable game so I can play it anywhere.
5. As a user, I want to improve my memory so I can do better in school.
6. As a user, I want to play a game that’s easy to learn so I can teach it to my young children.
7. As a user, I want to improve my memory so I can enhance my cognitive abilities.
8. As a user, I want to play with my grandparents so I can spend more time with them. 
9. As a user, I want to have a game to play when the power goes out so I don’t get bored.
10. As a user, I want a new game to play with my girlfriend in quarantine so we have something new to play.